---
import MainLayout from '../../../layouts/MainLayout.astro';
import MotuSidebar from '../../../components/MotuSidebar.astro';
const title = "Modeled Analog EQ";
---
<MainLayout title={title}>
  <div class="flex gap-8 items-start">
    <div class="w-[250px] flex-shrink-0">
      <MotuSidebar />
    </div>
    <article class="prose max-w-none">
      <h1>{title}</h1>
      <p>Source: <a href="https://motu.com/products/motuaudio/ultralite-mk3/cuemix-fx-overview.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener">MOTU product page</a></p>
      <p>The modeled analog EQ emulates classic analog curves to shape tone with musical results. It’s available within the DSP effects suite for both corrective and creative tonal shaping during monitoring or tracking.</p>
      <figure>
        <img src="/assets/motu/ultralite-mk3/modeled-eq.jpg" alt="Modeled analog EQ" />
        <figcaption>Absolute asset path: C:\\www\\dexgear\\public\\assets\\motu\\ultralite-mk3\\modeled-eq.jpg</figcaption>
      </figure>
    </article>
  </div>
</MainLayout>
